[silent_push_indicator://<name>]
global_account = Select the silent push account for which you want to collect data.
interval = Time interval of input.
index = Select the index in which data should be collected. Only required if "Collection Type" is set to \"Index\".
threat_intelligence_type = Select the type to collect the data for Threat Intelligence.
silent_push_feed_uuid = Enter silent push threat intelligence feed UUID.
silent_push_filter_profile = Enter silent push threat intelligence filter profile UUID.
data_export_url = Enter silent push threat intelligence data export URL.
feed_scanner_url = Enter silent push threat intelligence organization exports URL.
iofa_exports_url = Enter silent push threat intelligence IOFA Exports URL.
